two sometimes crassly opposed types

00:09:07.550 --> 00:09:15.250
of musical [inaudible], and each of
these types of [inaudible] develop

00:09:15.250 --> 00:09:18.210
in its particular way over
the course of the piece,

00:09:18.210 --> 00:09:21.970
but [inaudible] take
incognizance of what the other sort

00:09:21.970 --> 00:09:24.780
