00:17:54.170 --> 00:18:00.690
but when that activity disappears
and time is left in a sort

00:18:00.690 --> 00:18:07.910 position:56%
of naked form as a polyphonic sort
of counter entity with the material,

00:18:07.910 --> 00:18:10.380
that's the moment when we
perceive time most [inaudible],

00:18:10.380 --> 00:18:15.310
and that's always been
something that fascinates me.

00:18:15.310 --> 00:18:19.930
&gt;&gt; David Phylar: Well the work
